    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were formally assessed; all six remaining factors are acceptable at MRL 2 without full assessment. The overall assurance level is declared Medium, reflecting satisfactory performance across the assessed factor set and compliance with MRL 2 requirements. The model is deemed sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission decision.",
